{
  "title": "Mac 关闭 Dashboard 开机 更快",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">在 Mac OS 里一项功能叫作 Dashboard, 透过 Dashboard 所提供的各种小工具 Widget , 让我们可以很方便地取得特定的资讯。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">不过亦有不少人极少甚至不使用 Dashboard 的, 与其没有用途, 倒不如将它从内存中解放出来, 让小 Mac 启动及运作得更快吧！</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">如何将 Dashboard 关闭掉呢？</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">现在我们一起试试吧。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">1. 在“应用程式”&amp;gt;“工具程式”内执行“终端机”</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: large; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA;\">2. 在终端机视窗输入</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">defaults write com.apple.dashboard mcx-disabled -boolean YES</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">然后按 Enter 执行</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">3. 再输入</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">killall Dock</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">然后按 Enter 执行</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">Dashboard 便会关闭, 怎么呼唤它也没用了, 不过启动小 Mac 的时间又缩短了, 内存也节省了 ^_^</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">如果你想再次启动 Dashboard 的话, 只要在终端机执行</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">defaults write com.apple.dashboard mcx-disabled -boolean NO</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, HELVETICA; font-size: large; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">以及 killall Dock 便可</span>"
    }
  ]
}